rows.label: qst701307_msg0001
rows.name:
I don't know where Leon
went. I have no choice but
to rely on you all...

rows.label: qst701307_msg0002
rows.name:
The Rainbow Blossom doesn't bloom in
ordinary places. I think there might be
some in a secret, hard-to-reach location.

rows.label: qst701307_msg0003
rows.name:
I never thought he'd actually go
looking for something like that.

rows.label: qst701307_msg0004
rows.name:
If something happened to
him... it's my fault.
